detailIntroText: Farcana is a shooter game with a battle royale mode, where players seek to start a new life on a terraformed Mars and earn Infilium—the most powerful resource in the galaxy—to create disruptive technologies and mine Bitcoin with extra speed. Farcana is backed by the patented deflationary Play-to-Hash economic model based on real Bitcoin mining power.
introduceText: Shooter game with a battle royale mode
